Just days after his comments about Paramount, Stephen Colbert began The Late Show by announcing that it had been cancelled ‚Äî it will run until May 2026 before ending for good."It's not just the end of our show, but it's the end of The Late Show on CBS," Colbert told the shocked audience. "I'm not being replaced. This is all just going away."3. Stephen Colbert ramping up his coverage of Trump and Epstein

